#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.expand_dims"
msgstr "# triton.language.expand_dims"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:4
msgid "在指定轴位置插入大小为1的维度，不改变张量的数据，仅增加维度数。支持负索引，从右向左计数。"
msgstr "Insert a dimension of size 1 at the specified axis position without changing the tensor's data, only increasing the number of dimensions. Supports negative indexing, counting from right to left."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.expand_dims(input, axis)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `input.expand_dims(axis)` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.expand_dims(input, axis)` - function call form\n"
"- `input.expand_dims(axis)` - member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Function:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:12
msgid ""
"- 在指定轴位置插入大小为1的维度\n"
"- 不改变张量的数据，仅增加维度数\n"
"- 支持负索引，从右向左计数\n"
msgstr ""
"- Insert a dimension of size 1 at the specified axis position  \n"
"- Does not change the tensor data, only increases the number of dimensions  \n"
"- Supports negative indexing, counting from right to left\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | 是 | 输入张量 |\n"
"| axis | int \\| Tuple[int] | 是 | 插入维度的位置，支持负索引 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|----------|-------------|\n"
"| input | tensor | Yes | Input tensor |\n"
"| axis | int \\| Tuple[int] | Yes | Position to insert the dimension, supports negative indexing |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 在指定axis位置插入大小为1的维度\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 通过tensor::ExpandShapeOp实现，无数据拷贝\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor  \n"
"- **Shape:** Inserts a dimension of size 1 at the specified axis position  \n"
"- **Data Type:** Same as the input tensor  \n"
"- **Memory Layout:** Implemented via `tensor::ExpandShapeOp`, no data copy\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:24
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/expand_dims.md:26
msgid ""
"- axis必须在[-rank-1, rank]范围内，其中rank为输入张量的维度数\n"
"- 插入的维度大小固定为1\n"
msgstr ""
"- axis must be within the range [-rank-1, rank], where rank is the number of dimensions of the input tensor\n"
"- The size of the inserted dimension is fixed at 1\n"

